data.description: JUST REDUCED!!! Owner is also offering up to $10,000 in seller concessions.     Welcome to your dream waterfront oasis! Nestled in the serene community of South Gulf Cove, this home offers an outstanding coastal living experience. With beautiful views of the Autry Waterway, this property promises amazing sunsets as you relax on the canal side dock or the deck of the heated salt water pool. This would make a great home or rental opportunity..  Enjoy direct access to the water from this prime Waterfront location, stepping from your backyard to the oversized composite dock, perfect for boating, fishing or cruising through the miles of the South Gulf Cove canal system.This tastefully decorated home boasts three bedrooms and two baths offering ample space and the split bedroom layout provides privacy for your family and guests. A newly screened pool lanai  is ideal for entertaining while you BBQ, relax or watch passing boats and wildlife known throughout the community. A new roof and central air system was installed in 2023.       You'll notice the care that was put into this home from the beautiful quartz countertops in the kitchen to the wood plank vinyl flooring throughout most of the house. A spacious living room area and dining room lead to your heated salt water pool in the back lanai and down to the dock at the waterline. The main bedroom has its own sliding glass doorway to the pool area and a huge private bath behind sliding barn doors. Walk right in to the open shower area with an oversized shower panel system. The Dual vanity sinks are an added bonus to this  to round out this room! The garage floor has been freshly painted and the walls are finished and painted to create a great workshop or fitness room!      South Gulf Cove is renowned for its community amenities offering residents access to the Community Boat Ramp to launch your boat or kayak as well as several Parks and playground areas. Situated in the heart of Southwest Florida, South Gulf Cove offers easy access to the stunning beaches of Manasota Key, Boca Grande and Venice Beach. World famous Siesta Key can be reached in less than an hour. Numerous Golf Courses, shopping, dining and entertainment options are conveniently located nearby including the new Allegiant Sunseeker Resort,Savor featuring the flavors of 20 original world-class food & beverage concepts — from fine dining destinations to casual eateries, local ingredients to global influences.       This waterfront home is an exceptional opportunity to embrace an amazing Florida lifestyle, don't miss your chance to call this slice of paradise your own! Flood Insurance can transfer to new owners!
